1> create a employee.jsp page(ems-employee)
2> create a Employee.java class
3> create business method setEmployee() method
	which will do the save the employee to db
4> create showEmployee.jsp 
which will have<jsp:useBean> action where
u will use <jsp:setProperty> and
also call business method by using <jsp:setProperty>
then display employee details using <jsp:getProperty>